headline.print_headline: Airbus Faces Tough Battles Over A330 Longevity Plan
headline.main: Airbus Faces Tough Battles Over A330 Longevity Plan

lead_paragraph: As Airbus races through flight testing of its newest plane, the next-generation A350, Europe's planemaker faces growing battles to secure a future for the A330, until now its only truly lucrative wide-body jet.
